<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>No_such_file on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/no_such_file/</link><description>Recent content in No_such_file on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/no_such_file/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>[Solution] Ruby Errno::ENOENT — No such file or directory Fix</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/ruby/file-not-found/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/ruby/file-not-found/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="errnoenoent--no-such-file-or-directory-fix"&gt;Errno::ENOENT — No such file or directory Fix&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An &lt;code&gt;Errno::ENOENT&lt;/code&gt; is raised when a file or directory operation references a path that doesn&amp;rsquo;t exist.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="description"&gt;Description&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;Errno::ENOENT&lt;/code&gt; (Error NO ENTry) is the most common file system error. It means the operating system cannot find the file or directory at the specified path.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Common scenarios:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;File doesn&amp;rsquo;t exist&lt;/strong&gt; — typo in filename or wrong directory.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Directory doesn&amp;rsquo;t exist&lt;/strong&gt; — trying to read from a missing directory.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Symlink broken&lt;/strong&gt; — symbolic link points to non-existent target.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Case sensitivity&lt;/strong&gt; — &lt;code&gt;File.txt&lt;/code&gt; vs &lt;code&gt;file.txt&lt;/code&gt; on Linux.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-ruby" data-lang="ruby"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Cause 1: File doesn&amp;#39;t exist&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;File&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;read(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;config.yml&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;) &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Errno::ENOENT: No such file or directory&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Cause 2: Wrong path&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;File&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;read(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;src/main.rb&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;) &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Errno::ENOENT if path is incorrect&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Cause 3: Directory doesn&amp;#39;t exist&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;Dir&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;entries(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;/nonexistent/dir&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;) &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Errno::ENOENT&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Cause 4: Broken symlink&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;File&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;read(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;link_to_missing&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;) &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Errno::ENOENT if target doesn&amp;#39;t exist&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="solutions"&gt;Solutions&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="fix-1-check-file-existence-before-access"&gt;Fix 1: Check file existence before access&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-ruby" data-lang="ruby"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Wrong&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;data &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;File&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;read(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;config.yml&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Correct&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;File&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;exist?(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;config.yml&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; data &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;File&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;read(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;config.yml&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;else&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; puts &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Config file not found, using defaults&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; data &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; default_config
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;end&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-2-use-beginrescue-for-graceful-handling"&gt;Fix 2: Use begin/rescue for graceful handling&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-ruby" data-lang="ruby"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Wrong&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;config &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;File&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;read(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;config.yml&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Correct&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;begin&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; config &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;File&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;read(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;config.yml&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;rescue&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;Errno&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;ENOENT&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; config &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; default_config
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;end&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-3-verify-paths-with-filedirectory"&gt;Fix 3: Verify paths with File.directory?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-ruby" data-lang="ruby"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Wrong&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;Dir&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;entries(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;/path/to/dir&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;) &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Errno::ENOENT&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Correct&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;dir_path &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;/path/to/dir&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;File&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;directory?(dir_path)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; entries &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;Dir&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;entries(dir_path)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;else&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; puts &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Directory not found: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;#{&lt;/span&gt;dir_path&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;end&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-4-use-fileexpand_path-for-absolute-paths"&gt;Fix 4: Use File.expand_path for absolute paths&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-ruby" data-lang="ruby"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Wrong — relative path depends on working directory&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;File&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;read(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;data.txt&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Correct — use absolute path&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;data_path &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;File&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;expand_path(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;../data.txt&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, __FILE__)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;File&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;exist?(data_path)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; data &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;File&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;read(data_path)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;end&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="permission-denied"&gt;Errno::EACCES&lt;/a&gt; — permission denied.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="load-error"&gt;LoadError&lt;/a&gt; — cannot load such file.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="io-error"&gt;IOError&lt;/a&gt; — stream closed or invalid I/O.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>